{
  "chapter": 31,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十一回 漫天要价。叶开离开冷香园，带着多尔甲遗物——青铜面具和玉牌，来到延平门城门口摆摊，打出\"高价出售，货卖识家\"的招牌。城西十宝斋的宋老板被马车中躲藏的神秘人胁迫，前来代购玉牌。叶开先开价三万两，宋老板拿出银票欲买，叶开却坐地起价至三十万两，再涨至三百万两，将宋老板气昏。叶开识破真正买家是车厢中的神秘人，直接喊话邀其出面。车厢中人冷笑回应，派出一个九尺半的铁塔巨人攻击叶开。叶开以言语戏弄巨人，趁其暴怒冲来时反肘将其击倒，又制服了从背后偷袭的宋老板，夺下马车追击神秘人。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "中年人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这是不是要卖的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "中年人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这块玉倒是汉玉，只可惜雕工差了点。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "text": "非但雕工差了些，玉也不太好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "中年人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你这人做生意倒还很老实。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "text": "我这人本来就老实。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "中年人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "却不知你想卖什么价钱？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "text": "高价。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "中年人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "高价是多少。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "text": "你不妨先出个价钱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "中年人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "三十两怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "中年人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这价钱我虽已出得太高了些，可是君子一言，我也不想再杀你的价。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "text": "三十两？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "中年人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "十足十的纹银三十两。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "text": "你是想买哪一样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "中年人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "当然是这块玉牌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "text": "三十两却只能买这根竹竿。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "中年人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你想要多少？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "text": "三万两！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "中年人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "三万两？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "text": "十足十的纹银三万两。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "text": "这块玉牌的玉质虽然不太好，雕工也很差，可是你若要买，就得出三万两，少一文我都不卖。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "宋老板",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "现在我是不是已可将这块玉牌拿走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "text": "不行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "宋老板",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "为什么还不行。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "text": "因为价钱不对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "宋老板",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你刚才岂非说好的三万两？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "text": "那是刚才的价钱。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "宋老板",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "现在呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "text": "现在要三十万两。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "宋老板",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "三十万两？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "text": "这块玉并不好，雕工也差，可是现在无论谁要买，都得三十万两，少一文也不卖。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_che_xiang_zhong_ren",
      "text": "你现在已肯出三十万两？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "宋老板",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "三十万就三十万。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "宋老板",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你笑什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "text": "我在笑你。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "宋老板",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "笑我。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "text": "我在笑你刚才为什么不买。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "宋老板",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "现在……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "text": "现在的价钱跟刚才又不一样了，现在要三百万两，少一文都不卖。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "宋老板",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "三百万两？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "宋老板",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你……你……你简直是个强盗。你好黑的心。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_song_lao_ban",
      "text": "你若认为这价钱太高，可以不买，我并没有勉强你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_che_xiang_zhong_ren",
      "text": "阁下既然想要这东西，为什么自己不来买？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_che_xiang_zhong_ren",
      "text": "阁下若肯自己出面，我也许一文都不要，就奉送给阁下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_che_xiang_zhong_ren",
      "speaker_name": "车厢中人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_che_xiang_zhong_ren",
      "text": "我是个老实人，我从不说假话。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_che_xiang_zhong_ren",
      "speaker_name": "车厢中人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ju_ren",
      "text": "你有多高？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ju_ren",
      "speaker_name": "巨人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "九尺半。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ju_ren",
      "text": "九尺半的确已不能算矮。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ju_ren",
      "speaker_name": "巨人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "比我再高的人，这世上只怕还没有几个。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ju_ren",
      "text": "兵器是讲究一寸长，一寸强，你若是杆枪，一定是杆好枪。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ju_ren",
      "speaker_name": "巨人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我不是枪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ju_ren",
      "text": "还有很多别的东西，也是以长短来分贵贱的，譬如说，长的竹竿就比短的贵，所以你若是根竹竿，一定也很值钱。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ju_ren",
      "text": "只可惜你也不是竹竿。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ju_ren",
      "speaker_name": "巨人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我是人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ju_ren",
      "text": "就因为你是人，所以实在可惜得很。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ju_ren",
      "speaker_name": "巨人",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "有什么可惜？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ju_ren",
      "text": "只有人是从不以长短轻重来分贵贱的，一个人的四肢若是太发达，头脑就往往会很简单，所以越长的人，往往反而越不值钱。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 394
    }
  ],
